reviews.review_text: Top 5 of '79 This is a legendary show for good reason.  Great tunes, and great sound quality thanks to Barry G!

live dead saw this show with my good friend "slats"man those were the days!this was a make up show,and i'm so glad i made it then and am are able to listen now,hahaha igotto go,peace and love all you groovy cats,much very large hunks of brownies to you cats that hook us up here with these tunes,mahalo,kidos!!!
